   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 100 families in Kilembe Community recover</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A heavy down pour hit Kilembe Mines villages and the surrounding Rwenzori ranges in Kasese District in Uganda on the night of the April 2013. This is the worst down pour that the region has experienced in the last 30 years or more. The project will provide emergency assistance and long term relief to those affected by the heavy down pour.</narrative>
